window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Evil’s been leveling up. Now the Master of Swords must rescue more Swordmaidens from the darkness before the world of Occida perishes!</b></p> <p>Dante Castillo’s had a wild ride since a goddess transported him to the fantasy world of Occida. As the chosen Master of Swords, he’s had to rescue Swordmaidens—powerful women magically bound to their realm’s most powerful magic sword—who were thought lost forever.</p> <p>Not only did he win their lives back, he also won their love.</p> <p>But the evil they faced down a century ago isn’t sleeping anymore. Dante’s going to have to locate and rescue two more Swordmaidens—a mysterious blade dancer and a combat-ready paladin!</p>"; 
